   <body>
      <context>
         <p>If you decide in the same session that you want to keep a field in the document that you have already marked for deletion, follow these steps.</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Fields</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Right-click on the field in the Document pane that you marked for deletion and select <uicontrol>Undo Delete</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Yes </uicontrol>on the confirmation dialog that appears. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
